trans-unit.source: Represents a single [Import](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/3bfecaf1-69fd-4008-b651-c9dafd4389d9) element in an MSBuild project.
trans-unit.target: Representa um elemento [Import](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/3bfecaf1-69fd-4008-b651-c9dafd4389d9) em um projeto do MSBuild.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <c>Condition</c> attribute value of the [Import](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/3bfecaf1-69fd-4008-b651-c9dafd4389d9) element.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o valor de atributo <c>Condition</c> do elemento [Import](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/3bfecaf1-69fd-4008-b651-c9dafd4389d9).

trans-unit.source: The <c>Condition</c> attribute value of the <c>Import</c> element.
trans-unit.target: O <c>condição</c> valor de atributo de <c>importação</c> elemento.

trans-unit.source: Gets the fully qualified path of the file specified in the <c>Name</c> attribute of the [Import](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/3bfecaf1-69fd-4008-b651-c9dafd4389d9) element.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o caminho totalmente qualificado do arquivo especificado no atributo <c>Name</c> do elemento [Import](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/3bfecaf1-69fd-4008-b651-c9dafd4389d9).

trans-unit.source: The fullly qualified path of the file specified in the <c>Name</c> attribute of the <c>Import</c> element.
trans-unit.target: O caminho fullly qualificado do arquivo especificado no <c>nome</c> atributo do <c>importação</c> elemento.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the [Import](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/3bfecaf1-69fd-4008-b651-c9dafd4389d9) element was imported into the project.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se o elemento [Import](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/3bfecaf1-69fd-4008-b651-c9dafd4389d9) foi importado para o projeto.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <c>Import</c> element was imported into the project; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Se o <c>importação</c> elemento foi importado para o projeto; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <c>Project</c> attribute value of the [Import](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/3bfecaf1-69fd-4008-b651-c9dafd4389d9) element.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o valor do atributo <c>Project</c> do elemento [Import](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/3bfecaf1-69fd-4008-b651-c9dafd4389d9).

trans-unit.source: The <c>Project</c> attribute value of the <c>Import</c> element.
trans-unit.target: O <c>projeto</c> valor de atributo de <c>importação</c> elemento.
